---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Terms of Use — InfoOnVisa" noindex={true}>
  <div class="wrap prose">
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: 21 June 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Information only, not advice</h2>
    <p>InfoOnVisa provides AI-assisted travel and visa information for general guidance only. It is not legal, immigration, or financial advice. You are responsible for verifying all details with official government sources before acting.</p>

    <h2>2. Accuracy</h2>
    <p>We aim for accuracy and date each page, but visa rules change frequently and we make no warranty that content is complete, current, or error-free.</p>

    <h2>3. Third-party links</h2>
    <p>We link to official portals and may link partner services. We are not responsible for the content or practices of third-party sites. Some links may be affiliate links from which we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.</p>

    <h2>4. Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, InfoOnVisa is not liable for any loss arising from reliance on information on this site.</p>

    <h2>5. Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update these terms at any time. Continued use constitutes acceptance of the current terms.</p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .prose { max-width: 720px; padding: 40px 20px; }
  .prose h1 { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .prose h2 { font-size: 19px; margin: 24px 0 8px; }
  .prose p { margin-bottom: 10px; }
</style>
